snippet.title: A Soldier's Reaction. #Holiday #shorts
snippet.description:
A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under his command.
Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sonakshi Sinha, Freddy Daruwala 
Directed by - A.R. Murugadoss


"Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a high-octane action film which showcases Akshay Kumar's skills as an action star. The movie boasts of thrilling and intense action sequences, a well-written screenplay, and good performances from the lead actors. The plot of the movie revolves around the life of a soldier on vacation who stumbles upon a terrorist plot and decides to put a stop to it. He has to work with a local police officer and other officials to track down the terrorists and prevent them from carrying out their plan. The film also deals with themes of patriotism and selfless service to the nation. Overall, "Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a well-crafted action thriller that is sure to keep audiences on the edge of their seats.
#holiday #akshaykumar #sonakshisinha #govinda #freddydaruwala #soldier #shorts

snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd.

snippet.description:
Meri Bassai is one of the longest and most popular Nepali comedy serials with 18 Years of broadcasting. Based on rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people, the series represents many political and social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavor. It is aired in Nepal Television at 8:50 PM and in YouTube at 9:30 PM every Tuesday. This show is produced by Media Hub Pvt. Ltd. 

The story is based on the rural lifestyle and lower-middle-class people. The show represents many political as well as social issues on its episodes with educational comedy flavour.

snippet.title: Shops with NO Shopkeepers! Have seen this?
snippet.description:
Across New Zealand, you'll find unmanned shops that are based on honesty. Kiwi farmers set up stalls on the roadside outside their homes and sell their fruit and vegetables for low prices directly to motorists. The farmer isn't at the stall, though! An honesty box is there where customers leave the correct amount for what they take.

At this stall in Northland, we bought two bags of avocados for just $4. Does this happen in your country? We've also heard this happens in Mizoram, India.

An honesty box is there where customers leave the correct amount for what they take.

At this stall in Northland, we bought two bags of avocados for just $4. Does this happen in your country? We've also heard this happens in Mizoram, India.
